cs.LO, cs.AI, cs.GT, cs.MA, cs.IT 

This paper deals with epistemic logic and the study of knowledge in groups, which falls under the category of logic (cs.LO). It also involves the concept of communication and information sharing, which is relevant to artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the relationship between distributed and common knowledge, which is a topic in game theory (cs.GT) and multi-agent systems (cs.MA). Finally, the paper introduces a new operator for resolving distributed knowledge, which has implications for information theory (cs.IT).
